{"tid":1999026,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【歷史台】我又出新文章喇，今次講魁北克獨立運動","createTime":"2020-05-03T01:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T14:21:50.000Z","uid":120678,"like":85,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"174d5370d769b38983f9222cad9f5f9e667cee6e","tid":1999026,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T01:00:26.000Z","msg":"如果問我點解要寫呢個系列文章，主要係因為見到近年關於香港前途既討論越來越多<br />\n有d人會選擇支持永續基本法，有人選擇要求歸英，有人想建立華夏邦聯，有人想自決，亦都有人想獨立建國<br />\n我寫魁北克既經驗，並唔係想帶出一個確切既結論，關於香港前途既論述，小弟亦自知冇咁既實力去加磚添瓦<br />\n但係我希望做既係，從魁北克既經驗去比大家反思，點解魁北克由和理非，到勇武，再回歸和理非，再到1980年同1995年兩次公投<br />\n可能好多人都未必知，加拿大既法裔為左唔想捲入英國人既戰爭，曾經「火魔」「私了」樣樣出齊<br />\n中間到底發生左乜事，英殖民/加拿大政府又點樣由早期開槍殺人，到坐響談判桌上心平氣和咁談判<br />\n當然，加拿大既經驗唔一定適用於香港，中共亦都唔係加國政府，但透過呢段歷史，希望可以刺激讀者思考，帶起討論<br />\n入正題<br />\n<br />\n目前《魁北克歷史》系列呢個文章係響Fortune Insight雜誌連載，逢週四出文，上篇係第2集<br />\n先講講已經出左既文：<br />\n<br />\n第一集：《法屬北美的拓荒史》(4月23日已推出)<br />\n<img src=\"https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kanada-monreal-montreal-doma-414x217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprime.fortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Fkanada-monreal-montreal-doma-414x217.jpg&h=1315cb8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/483124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprime.fortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F483124&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjguIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=da2f8621\" target=\"_blank\">https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/483124</a><br />\n第二集：《七年戰爭和殖民地的易手》(4月30日已推出)<br />\n<img src=\"https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/maxresdefault-2-414x217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprime.fortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Fmaxresdefault-2-414x217.jpg&h=608d9d34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/483382\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprime.fortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F483382&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjguIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=29ac6603\" target=\"_blank\">https://prime.fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/483382</a><br />\n<br />\n以下係已起左稿但未發佈既文：<br />\n<br />\n第三集：《1837-38年的革命和加拿大聯邦的成立》(預計5月7日推出)<br />\n第四集：《1917年和1944年徵兵令危機》(預計5月14日推出)<br />\n第五集：《60年代繁榮但躁動不安的城市：滿地可》(預計5月21日推出)<br />\n第六集：《魁北克人黨的成立和魁獨運動的興起》(預計5月28日推出)<br />\n第七集：《1980年的第一次獨立公投》(預計6月4日推出)<br />\n第八集：《1995年的第二次獨立公投》(預計6月11日推出)<br />\n第九集：《2000年至今：魁北克獨立運動的現況》(預計6月18日推出)<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有興趣可以入左去link度睇下先，亦都歡迎響呢個post度討論<br />\n再一次謝謝大家長期以來既支持，亦都多謝連登學術台比到我一個空間去討論"},{"pid":"03e4f61e293a3b0a339bc5b25634667dc394c7f1","tid":1999026,"uid":271157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T03:01:48.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14163001e7cd9bbe555e59a2bc2712a9d590786","tid":1999026,"uid":254456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4cecdeb6d4ecbc1c7b27e3e2d7e9a0ecd0927a","tid":1999026,"uid":254456,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T06:00:24.000Z","msg":"真心唔明點解巴打你啲文章咁高質<br />\n<br />\n都好似冇乜人睇咁樣 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41b62c07af4e05c25e15cbdd7265c5d87267f56","tid":1999026,"uid":253444,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T06:48:54.000Z","msg":"LM <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a26f3c6475acfc4d7be13d08d0b59794299c5da","tid":1999026,"uid":8681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T06:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as