r />\n樓上個回覆令我諗起 娛樂至死"},{"pid":"b6b82b2efb58197bc72ba1139a5a1f7dde047667","tid":1999026,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:21:37.000Z","msg":"好文未睇先推"},{"pid":"80ea9a64b25dffe3fce54fbfa4794b4b5c6c651b","tid":1999026,"uid":262406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:23:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef2df8972cb4677421aa4a7cc7b2fc5721d3ff59","tid":1999026,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:17:48.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b935fa74a17abfd1ec0ccd51d73bd44950bd7a7b","tid":1999026,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:52:39.000Z","msg":"隔離post有人問我羅馬史入門睇咩書好，我覆左果位網友<br />\n覺得呢個post可能都有人有相同既疑問，所以將我既回覆轉貼過黎<br />\n<blockquote>吉本《羅馬帝國衰亡史》可以用黎當參考書，但個人唔建議一開始就睇<br />\n因為吉本距今已經二百幾年，呢二百幾年間有好多新既考古研究成果<br />\n而吉本既年代未有咁多考古成果，佢寫書時只係靠文獻證據<br />\n所以部分關於羅馬史領域係有機會有部分認知同現代學術界有差別<br />\n如果真係入門想睇關於羅馬史既書，建議睇d比較新既學術著作<br />\n例如The Cambridge Ancient History、The Oxford Handbook of Roman Studies<br />\n其實我都冇睇曬上面兩本書，但睇過The Oxford Handbook of the Bronze Age Aegean<br />\n佢每個chapter都由該領域既專家同學術權威寫，我會推薦咁睇多過一黎就直接睇吉本</blockquote><br />\n希望我既經驗分享可以幫到對古典史感興趣既大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfc22ff8f045dfdcf7a81ca409ac11eca7f8f69","tid":1999026,"uid":34075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:55:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47bd792bc5169fab318418a54aad962ebe66a113","tid":1999026,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41139169a03893f9e4a54a59cfa6ea90b6a12f43","tid":1999026,"uid":95516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41373f20ef3b55ecd559d0298e89fa6f8a64494f","tid":1999026,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51ea22076f020b83a3616da75cc9fd4dc8e2ec9f","tid":1999026,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T14:41:09.000Z","msg":"想知猶太人歷史<br />\n有無咩書推介<br />\n100-200頁左右既中文書<br />